    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a showroom-quality car. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and zero issues. Buyers can expect a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
